put.description:
更新 Access Key 信息

用法示例：
```
PUT /api/v1/auth/ak/{ak_id}
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "新的AK名称",
    "description": "新的描述",
    "is_active": true
}
```

delete.description:
删除 Access Key

用法示例：
```
DELETE /api/v1/auth/ak/{ak_id}
Authorization: Bearer {token}
```
